moved\">window</i>\r\ndi <b>indo-emmg-01</b>, sebagai <b xss=\"removed\"><i xss=\"removed\">supervis</i></b></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">·<span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=\"removed\">Masuk ke\r\ndirektori ~/<b>bin</b></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">·<span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=\"removed\">Ketik <b>SetBouq</b>\r\n<enter></enter></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Entry hex(ca-subid): <enter></enter></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Entry the Bouquet (w\'out zero): <enter></enter></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">·<span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=\"removed\">Pada perintah\r\ninput diatas, masukkan CA subs id, lalu masukkan Bouquet-ID.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</